It's easiest to think of this discipline as a workflow for creating mistakes. ^green;At their core, all traps rely on a victim making at least one mistake.^reset;

Making mistakes easy for your guests without exposing yourself to the same pitfalls ^#888888;(literally or figuratively)^reset; can make the difference between an adventurer escaping with your treasure or enriching your treasury!
